    },
    {
      "end": 173.86000061035156,
      "text": "teammate, we all die too. I'm sorry you're choosing this view, because you're no better than anyone",
      "start": 159.8800048828125
    },
    {
      "end": 182.16000366210938,
      "text": "you know. But I'm gonna tell you this one time, if you're in the zone, you ask for help and if you're",
