    {
      "end": 238.9199981689453,
      "text": "You think your time's a little fast, you think you got more, gotta make it last then. 1.5 seconds, it's over. Did you tell your loved ones, you loved them, because it all goes away.",
      "start": 224.82000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 258.8800048828125,
      "text": "Whether you hold on, you throw it, or you just walk, it all goes away. So treasure that life, and treasure your ride, to find the things that make you happy.",
